Package: inferit
Type: Package
Version: 0.3.1
Title: Hypothesis Tests and Statistical Distributions for 'SciViews::R'
Description: Statistical distributions (including their visual representation)
  and hypothesis tests with rich-formatted tabular outputs for the 'SciViews::R'
  dialect.
